 RPAD & LPAD :- 
 ----------------------
 
  => these functions are used to fill string with a character

     RPAD(string,length,char)       =>   fills on right side
     LPAD(string,length,char)        =>   fills  on left side

Ex :- 

    RPAD('HELLO',10,'*')	 =>	HELLO*****
    LPAD('HELLO',10,'*')	 =>	*****HELLO
    RPAD('*',10,'*')                       =>             **********

