 How to implement loop in SQL :-
 ---------------------------------------------
   
   SELECT  level
   FROM DUAL
   CONNECT BY  level <= 10 ; 

 => level is a system variable
 => level initialized with 1
 => by default level is incremented by 1
 => if cond = true  level is printed 
 => if cond = false loop ends

  level = 1 ;				level=1;
  CONNECT BY (level<=10)                                       WHILE(level <= 10)
  {                                                                                 {
      select level                                                                print level
      level = level + 1                                                         level = level + 1
  )                                                                                  }

 
